  <prompt>
    Filed 2026-05-26 as a W-6 follow-up after task 041's consumer audit found
    `src/solutions/LegalWorkspace/src/components/Shell/WorkspaceGrid.tsx:432`
    still calls `Xrm.Navigation.navigateTo` to `sprk_corporateworkspace?mode=todo`
