    **replace with an inline ToDo modal rendered within the SpaarkeAi shell**
    (consistent with the SpaarkeAi-is-host framing from W-1 / DR-01).
  </prompt>

  <role>
    SPAARKE platform developer. UX-aware refactor: the new modal should preserve
    the existing ToDo behavior the standalone page provided (same data shape,
    same filters, same actions) but render inline. No new domain logic â€” just
    component placement migration.
  </role>

  <goal>
    `WorkspaceGrid.tsx:432` no longer invokes `Xrm.Navigation.navigateTo` to
    `sprk_corporateworkspace`. Instead, opens a new SpaarkeAi modal component
    that renders the equivalent ToDo experience. The new modal is a self-
    contained React component in `@spaarke/legal-workspace` (or `SpaarkeAi`
    if context-specific) using Fluent v9 Dialog/Drawer primitives. Behavior
    parity with the retired page. No new BFF endpoint or service.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      W-6 retired the standalone `sprk_corporateworkspace` Code Page deploy
