      found one source-code reference that would 404 post-retirement.
      This task migrates that one consumer.

      Operator decision (OC-R4 follow-up, 2026-05-26): use an inline modal in
      the SpaarkeAi shell rather than removing the link entirely or building a
      compatibility shim. Rationale: preserves user-visible ToDo functionality;
      consistent with W-1's two-wrapper model (Direct widget wrapper category);
      avoids forcing the user out of the SpaarkeAi shell.
    </background>
